ee.ria.dhx.ws.service.impl

Class DhxPackageServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • ee.ria.dhx.ws.service.impl.DhxPackageServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DhxPackageService

    @Service(value="documentService")
public class DhxPackageServiceImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements DhxPackageService
    Class for document sending and receiving. Service is independent from capsule versions that are being sent or received, that means that no changes should be done in service if new capsule version is added.
    Author:
    Aleksei Kokarev
